documents.title: Common Issues
documents.summary: # Common Kubernetes Issues & Solutions ## CrashLoopBackOff **Symptom**: Pod status is `CrashLoopBackOff`. **Causes**: 1. Application error (check logs). 2. Misconfiguration (missing env vars, wrong config file). 3. Liveness probe failing. **Solution**: - Run `kubectl logs -p <pod>` to see previous logs. - Check exit code: `137` = OOM (increase limits), `1` = App Error. - Fix configuration or increase resources. ## ImagePullBackOff / ErrImagePull **Symptom**: Pod status is `ImagePullBackOff`....
